Let's look at the way in
which innovating industries,

00:39:27.460 --> 00:39:31.810
how do they spend when they're
trying to do major technology

00:39:31.810 --> 00:39:34.870
implementations?

00:39:34.870 --> 00:39:37.900
The semiconductor
industry invests 16%

00:39:37.900 --> 00:39:42.160
on average of annual
revenues in R&D.

